  "extras": {
    "summary": "AN ACT TO AMEND SECTION 43-11-13, MISSISSIPPI CODE OF 1972, TO REQUIRE THE STATE BOARD OF HEALTH TO ADOPT RULES REQUIRING THE STATE DEPARTMENT OF HEALTH TO DETERMINE COMPLIANCE WITH RULES FOR ELECTRICITY AND EMERGENCY POWER SOURCES OF NURSING FACILITIES AND ASSISTED LIVING FACILITIES DURING REGULAR UNANNOUNCED INSPECTIONS OF THOSE FACILITIES; AND FOR RELATED PURPOSES."
